<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>Returns the state ID eNoChange</para>
</simplesect>
Default implementation for OtaStart event handling. Derived classes may overload this default implementation. The function reject the start command by calling function otaStartReject of the <ref refid="class_fw_upd_ctrl" kindref="compound">FwUpdCtrl</ref> class instance. Pointer variable pd is assigned to <ref refid="class_fw_upd_ctrl" kindref="compound">FwUpdCtrl</ref> class instance. Finally function returns the state ID eNoChange. </para>
