    <briefdescription>
<para>State base class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The state base class provides a pointer to a data object, which normally is the this pointer of the state machine owner class, here this pointer of firmware update control task. It furthermore provides default implementations of the handler functions, which may be overridden by the derived state classes. All state classes of the firmware download statemachine shall be derived from this base class. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
